issue.title: [CF 1292] Last Ability Used conditional not working for DH skills
issue.body:
What steps will reproduce the problem?

Any spell cooldown with the conditional last ability used set to Fel Rush or Infernal Strike "matches or does not match"

What do you expect to happen? What happens instead?

Conditional does not trigger

What version of TellMeWhen are you using? ("The latest" is not a version)

8.1.2

Do you have an error log of what happened?

no errors, just icons do not reflect condition state

Please provide any additional information below (including any export strings if applicable; see above.)

any or all icons have this issue.


> Posted by CurseForge user ele5ion | Imported from CurseForge issue #1292 | Raw

comments.body:
Thanks. Fixed in g80f198f.


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
